Text: Thanks !! keep on seeding & Recommend to others!! :)
Great Torrent. All files work fine and sound great :)

Great quality TO THE NAKED EAR maybe...

What did you record this with variable bit rate? Terrible. It's worse than auto-volume-leveling. Some parts uber quiet where they shouldn't be, and some parts loud where they shouldn't be either.

All the tracks have different bit rates than eachother ~261. This could've all been better if ripped in 320kbps or other lossless format. But when you really listen to this stuff in headphones, you can hear the "tinny" sound of low-quality music.
